item.description: This new season marks one year that we started Hot Shots. We were lucky to have a good group of kids and parents grouped together. In this short time, the boys have gone from playing 6 v 6 to 9 v 9. This is a big jump, and while they're going to be playing at a higher level, it's time more thought is put into how the team is run.
